{"tid":1427293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"探討上國際法庭嘅可能性 搵國際人權律師幫手","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:44.000Z","uid":208543,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"428879911b270252e6fabb1b2d2fa11f8774a2cf","tid":1427293,"uid":208543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"幫朋友代po <br />\n<br />\n目前已經有420人被捕，還有數以千計受傷的記者，群眾，老弱婦孺。還有損壞的民居&hellip;等等。受害者與受害的家庭，不計其數。雖然我們有612人道基金，加上律師群。經過雨傘一役大家還相信香港的司法制度嗎? 就算有ICAC協助調查，大家相信嗎? 就算日後成立獨立調查委員會，大家相信嗎? 或許也是政府的緩兵之計。<br />\n<br />\n不如我們自行向國際求助，讓海牙國際法院變成是我們的獨立調查委員會吧。也讓海牙國際法院向共慘黨施壓。<br />\n<br />\n針對：警察濫權，濫用武力，政府策畫無差別恐襲，特赦被捕人士，並且幫無辜受傷的群眾，記者索償。<br />\n<br />\n以下有些人權律師的名單與機構，或許義務，或許我們可以眾籌打官司，用盡方法都要救出義士。連登有這麼多高手。可以大家一起想想。<br />\n<br />\nAmal Clooney : 成功向埃及政府施壓特赦記者 <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/36158436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F36158436&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=5f8f4088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/36158436</a><br />\n<br />\nLawyers Committee for International Human Rights<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.freedom-now.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.freedom-now.org%2F&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=f9264081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.freedom-now.org/</a><br />\n<br />\nAsia Justice and Rights<br />\nPatrick Burgess<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己的香港，自己救，香港人加油"},{"pid":"5a8cf970902c749290723b83db69735d97ef1c58","tid":1427293,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6f7a6008df2f0c8982ceef4fae305e05314e0f41","tid":1427293,"uid":34135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5c3402271eba4f99ffdc194bfef1e817a58c27","tid":1427293,"uid":1407